{"tid":472104,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[舉手指公]三星期順風車環冰島","createTime":"2017-11-18T01:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T13:52:44.000Z","uid":7131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"788127e20ce8683f6d534391f086c748471b74d2","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今年七月我就同女朋友兩個決定以截順風車，hitchhiking既方式黎玩冰島。一黎我地兩個都唔識揸車，冰島公共交通又唔想好方便，所以hitchhiking其實會比較flexible. 第二我地之前係美國都試過一次hitchhiking trip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，入正題先。其實出發前都係只大概列晒啲自己想睇既地方，再計劃一條路線。畢竟hitchhiking講運，好難預時間，呢個亦都係點解我地預三個星期既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路行一唔講啦！"},{"pid":"0d3a2f869efecb64b0d70c33cef9da09d3e97189","tid":472104,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"一路行一唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941ca1346ab248a50f825fe067f1cdb7082c38f5","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路行一唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92783a8990c649deb2432e582ecf4ba4d2b2d2d","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"Day 1 由Reykjavik入去Westfjord<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/094515_ccaed68f5f6b9fdd89f3a511fd8e59ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F094515_ccaed68f5f6b9fdd89f3a511fd8e59ad.jpg&h=eefcd898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWestfjord係我地今次旅程最想最想去既地方。Westfjord就係係地圖上西面好似隻手掌既地方，由於入面太多峽灣，啲路兜黎兜去，入去十分麻煩，所以一直唔算太多人會入去。俾個概念大家，同樣由首都出發，岩岩入到去Westfjord所需既時間同去北部最大城市Akureyri係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/095048_e69b77b68153cc03c6f5383b50e263ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F095048_e69b77b68153cc03c6f5383b50e263ea.jpg&h=46051e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日我地就搭巴士搭到離開首都最遠既個個站，係環冰島既主要公路Route 1上面開始截車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 截順風車最緊要就係心態，個人開心啲笑多啲，被人pick up既機會都大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果等左大約十分鐘，就有第一部車停了！佢地係一班台灣人，連後座擺滿行李都想執兩個位出黎俾我地坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果講講下先知其實大家目的地唔同，佢地去緊附近既一個國家公園，咁冇辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我地只要岩路既車都會上，預左要轉幾程先去到目的地。有車停低真係會令士氣大增<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住個半個鐘斷斷續續都有車停低，不過個個都唔同路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Westfjord真係咁少人去咩？！大約等多左15分鐘，就有一個當地叔叔話可以車我地大約三分一路程，我地梗係二話不說狗衝上車啦。同佢傾計先知，Westfjord其實連本地人都少去因為交通真係太麻煩，但真係係冰島最靚個part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路既風景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/100445_9573cb5cbbe8fb2e654f9e7205d17580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F100445_9573cb5cbbe8fb2e654f9e7205d17580.jpg&h=15b384f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/100446_9573cb5cbbe8fb2e654f9e7205d17580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F100446_9573cb5cbbe8fb2e654f9e7205d17580.jpg&h=f6fa3353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢啲路上等車其實都係一種享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經過幾程車，當中包括一個唔理道路安全既意佬，一個係blue lagoon附近地熱發電廠做既本地叔叔，終於黎到Westfjord既入口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/100825_e64ce85299835a1d11ca2de857e2705f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F100825_e64ce85299835a1d11ca2de857e2705f.jpg&h=54a49ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢刻真係幾感動，估唔到一開始就咁順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更諗唔到既係，我地等左大概5部車就有人肯載我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係公路等個陣見到，其實轉入呢條公路既車好少，十部大概得一部會轉入黎，而呢個鐘數會入去既車都好少，因為已經下午兩點了。載我地既都係遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路既風景其實好靚，但掛住傾計冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到一個分岔路，又係時間講byebye了。入左去之去發覺呢到真係與世隔絕咁，人同車都冇。等左10分鐘終於見到第一架車，而且停左！原來佢係住係前面個鎮既本地人，車住兩個B返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去個鎮都好呀，如果再截唔到車入去，都可以係個到扎營過一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4582d29768bc07ac3176fd0a9c39c42d0186fa1","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"食個早餐再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab7ce0e43f87cdc76506ae7d3dcd44d2ef7c241","tid":472104,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7668d17fad21fc7ae1bff285468d3bbf6117cf","tid":472104,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"乞車坐都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d比殺人魔車走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2d8dbbce67a16d4c5e582512589542dc31e01d","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乞車坐都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d比殺人魔車走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好啦咁我唔寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26f668985194a39e474a8dc6618454187c02052","tid":472104,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乞車坐都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d比殺人魔車走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好啦咁我唔寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續啦"},{"pid":"1d450835e6d4443070eaed31c909e8882f25ae48","tid":472104,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乞車坐都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d比殺人魔車走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好啦咁我唔寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗理d糞青<br />\n可能最遠淨係去過長洲"},{"pid":"3a59da0c8474e909688e899b2222603edc43cfcb","tid":472104,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"其實自己唔識揸車就一係學   一係唔好去啲唔自駕就唔好玩的地方   你咁樣又哂時間  又有危險性  順風車唔係大問題  問題係你好似一心諗住有車坐就去冰島   你估老憑一定車你咩......"},{"pid":"1bf18a54d8f6dd71a04a7eb75ae02ec5fa0f38ce","tid":472104,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乞車坐都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d比殺人魔車走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好啦咁我唔寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗理d糞青<br />\n可能最遠淨係去過長洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX777<br />\n<br />\n十卜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9e9cde68d346e7580ef8640467500eb64ebc00","tid":472104,"uid":18430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:56:09.000Z","msg":"試過去冰島坐順風車同車返人轉頭<br />\n老實講你最好強調下坐順風車既難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事呃咗啲靚仔同條女去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚有命案發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a328461b6e0cb71d84c3099023362cf917d548","tid":472104,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實自己唔識揸車就一係學   一係唔好去啲唔自駕就唔好玩的地方   你咁樣又哂時間  又有危險性  順風車唔係大問題  問題係你好似一心諗住有車坐就去冰島   你估老憑一定車你咩......</blockquote><br />\n其實順風車，好多鬼佬都好welcome<br />\n不過兩個人真係唔建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd09830d44413b859de8425d805fc393f16e695","tid":472104,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T21:09:37.000Z","msg":"正評係畀禾子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43e28c7fc21d2fb950c4f7279f1295b0e2cecc2","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實自己唔識揸車就一係學   一係唔好去啲唔自駕就唔好玩的地方   你咁樣又哂時間  又有危險性  順風車唔係大問題  問題係你好似一心諗住有車坐就去冰島   你估老憑一定車你咩......</blockquote><br />\n咁我係諗住學既，我純粹係鍾意呢種方式先至繼續姐，同埋我知會冇人車，所以都定左時間俾自己冇人車就上巴士。<br />\n至於揀冰島係因為知道個到基本上係最hitchhiker friendly既國家之一，所以先會full trip 順風車，如果去歐洲我就唔會啦"},{"pid":"d803cac46194454f73a0b479adbccf89aa1c6c32","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去冰島坐順風車同車返人轉頭<br />\n老實講你最好強調下坐順風車既難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事呃咗啲靚仔同條女去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚有命案發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7515f1e57f9d4edd395e91b5dc61553b4f60daec","tid":472104,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d803cac46194454f73a0b479adbccf89aa1c6c32","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去冰島坐順風車同車返人轉頭<br />\n老實講你最好強調下坐順風車既難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事呃咗啲靚仔同條女去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚有命案發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"繼續寫？"},{"pid":"318cf5cb251aa813be28474ad84787f7443201de","tid":472104,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4582d29768bc07ac3176fd0a9c39c42d0186fa1","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"食個早餐再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"食完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iceland.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd06f180d946696631ae7c84f4f7c06495ec3b9","tid":472104,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"驚水左啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}